---
---

<div class="editorial-box">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="editorial-header">
    <svg class="editorial-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
      <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10" />
    </svg>
    <h3 class="editorial-heading">Nos critères éditoriaux</h3>
  </div>

  <!-- Body -->
  <p class="editorial-text">
    At Tim Review, editorial reliability is our priority. We analyze each product independently, based on ingredient quality, practical use cases, pricing transparency and verified customer feedback. Every article is reviewed for accuracy, transparency and usefulness.
  </p>
  <p class="editorial-text editorial-text-light">
    Our goal is to give readers clear, useful information to make better health decisions. We do not accept payment to change our ratings.
  </p>
</div>

<style>
  .editorial-box {
    background-color: #f4f2ec;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .editorial-box { padding: 1.5rem; }
  }

  .editorial-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .editorial-icon {
    color: #ef7a1a;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .editorial-heading {
    font-family: 'Archivo', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 0.95rem + 0.25vw, 1.125rem);
    color: #242424;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .editorial-text {
    font-size: clamp(0.8125rem, 0.8rem + 0.1vw, 0.875rem);
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .editorial-text:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .editorial-text-light {
    color: #777;
  }
</style>
